[[rbtgo_depot_inscribe]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_depot_inscribe}

Inscribes a reliquary into the
{rbtgi_depot}:
mirrors upstream tool images into a datestamped GAR namespace
({rbtgog_depot}).

include::RBSDI-depot_inscribe.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_director_yoke]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_director_yoke}

Yokes a reliquary stamp across every vessel's
{rbrv_regime}:
validates the stamp once against GAR, then rewrites `RBRV_RELIQUARY` in every {rbrv_regime} file under `${RBRR_VESSEL_DIR}`
({rbtgog_depot}).

include::RBSDY-director_yoke.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_image_delete]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_image_delete}

Jettisons a single
{rbtgi_image}
artifact by
{rbst_locator}
({rbtgog_image}).
Locator-generic across hallmark members, reliquary tool images, and enshrinement images.

include::RBSIJ-image_jettison.adoc[]

[[rbtgo_image_retrieve]]
//axvo_method axd_transient axd_grouped
=== {rbtgo_image_retrieve}

Wrests a single
{rbtgi_image}
artifact by
{rbst_locator}
({rbtgog_image}).
Locator-generic across hallmark members, reliquary tool images, and enshrinement images.
{rbtr_director}-tier — peer to {rbtgo_image_delete}, distinct from {rbtgo_ark_summon}.

include::RBSIW-image_wrest.adoc[]

